title: Spider Silk
description:
The mysterious murderers who commit crimes frequently hide in the dark and stalk their prey silently! They may also stroll past innocent passers-by indifferently... or put up a kind smile, but wave a butcher's knife at the next moment! There's another possibility that... You're that murderer...

To read this in Tachiyomi, download the Cubari extension and search Cubari: gist/JOrfz
